highlights.title: Recognizing SVC Syndrome Symptoms
highlights.description: Key signs include facial swelling and neck vein engorgement.

highlights.title: Causes of SVC Syndrome
highlights.description: Small cell lung cancer and non-Hodgkin's lymphoma are major causes.

highlights.title: Effects of Increased Venous Pressure
highlights.description: Increased pressure leads to headaches and dyspnea.

highlights.title: Practice Question on Diagnosis
highlights.description: Engaging practice question reinforces learning about SVC syndrome.

highlights.title: Conclusion and Call to Action
highlights.description: Encourages viewers to like and subscribe for more content.
